All Implemented Interfaces:
ForwardTransferFunction<KeyForValue,KeyForStore>, TransferFunction<KeyForValue,KeyForStore>, NodeVisitor<TransferResult<KeyForValue,KeyForStore>,TransferInput<KeyForValue,KeyForStore>>
public class KeyForTransfer extends CFAbstractTransfer<KeyForValue,KeyForStore,KeyForTransfer>
KeyForTransfer ensures that java.util.Map.put and containsKey cause the appropriate @KeyFor annotation to be added to the key.
